txt.en: 'I've seen some hobgoblins in the camp here, but I think they are followers of Loknashra instead of Warlord Dushtalbúk because the Angmarim are teaching them necromantic rites! I don't need to tell you that's bad, [placeholder]. Put a stop to them before they get beyond the first few lessons of instruction and master their craft!'
Hobgoblin acolytes have been spotted learning necromancy from the Angmarim just outside the keep of Bagud-dum.\n\nYou should defeat hobgoblin acolytes.
Hórin can be found outside the dwarf-fort Bagud-dum.\n\nYou should talk to Hórin.

'How deep are these dealings between Loknashra and the Cult of Drugoth? I fear we may find out, [placeholder]. But for now you have done well to prevent the acolytes from becoming an even greater problem for the Gabil'akkâ!'
Hobgoblin followers of Loknashra have begun to learn necromancy from the Cult of Drugoth.
